<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2002/06/xhtml2"
      xmlns:xforms="http://www.w3.org/2002/xforms"
      xmlns:ev="http://www.w3.org/2001/xml-events"
      xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"
      xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema"
      xmlns:my="http://example.com"
      xml:lang="en">
  <head>
    <title>The action element (2)</title>

    <xforms:model id="mymodel">
        <xforms:instance>
	        <my:root>
                <my:test>10</my:test>
            </my:root>
	    </xforms:instance>
        <xforms:message level="modal" ev:event="xforms-rebuild">xforms-rebuild dispatched</xforms:message>
    </xforms:model>

  </head>
  <body>
    <h>The action element (2)</h>
    <p>Assertions tested by this test case:</p>
    <nl>
        <li href="!-- TBD: insert URI to assertion here">rebuild actions must be processed immediately.</li>
        <li href="!-- TBD: insert URI to assertion here">If a rebuild is flagged to occur and the rebuild action is processed, the rebuild action MUST NOT occur at the end of &lt;action&gt; processing.</li>
    </nl>

    <xforms:repeat nodeset="my:test">
        <xforms:input ref=".">
            <xforms:label>Test input</xforms:label>
        </xforms:input>
    </xforms:repeat>
            
    <xforms:trigger>
        <xforms:label>Run Test</xforms:label>
        <xforms:hint>Should dispatch an xforms-rebuild and then a message</xforms:hint>
        <xforms:action ev:event="xforms-activate">
            <xforms:insert nodeset="my:test" at="last()" position="after"/>
            <xforms:rebuild model="mymodel"/>
            <xforms:message level="modal">If xforms-rebuild was dispatched before this message and it won't be dispatched again after this message, the test is passed.</xforms:message>
        </xforms:action>
    </xforms:trigger>
    
  </body>
</html>
